/hpc2hdd/home/xhao390/py/urbanclip/data/: The image captures a serene rural landscape under a clear blue sky. A dirt road, the color of rich coffee, cuts through the scene, inviting the viewer's gaze to follow its path. On the left side of the road, a power line stands tall, a silent sentinel amidst the tranquility. The right side of the road is adorned with trees and shrubs, their leaves a vibrant green against the earthy tones of the road. The sun, a brilliant orb of light, shines brightly in the top right corner of the image, casting a warm glow over the scene. The image is taken from a low angle, adding a sense of depth and perspective to the view. The overall composition of the image suggests a peaceful coexistence between man-made structures and nature.
